room_title: Escape room "We're so F%#ked!" by Esscape Room in New York
room_description:
Imagine you are thrown into a very bad situation, and you have to - for lack of a better term - "UN-F%#CK YOURSELF!".

A tighter, darker, faster-paced ESScape Room. No one really knows what they are walking into... Difficulty levels are high, but the rewards are higher! In a little space, there is much to do. Plus, one of the most authentic, gritty sets in NYC!
